### Step 4: Validate

Run these commands in order:

1. `dotnet build sdk/cosmosdbforpostgresql/Azure.ResourceManager.CosmosDBForPostgreSql/`
2. `dotnet test sdk/cosmosdbforpostgresql/Azure.ResourceManager.CosmosDBForPostgreSql/ --filter TestCategory!=Live`
3. `eng/scripts/Update-Snippets.ps1 cosmosdbforpostgresql` — injects snippet code from `#region` tags into the README placeholders; verify the README diff looks correct
4. `eng/scripts/Export-API.ps1 cosmosdbforpostgresql` — regenerates public API listing if any public types changed
5. `dotnet format sdk/cosmosdbforpostgresql/Azure.ResourceManager.CosmosDBForPostgreSql/` — ensures consistent formatting

